      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t美国不枯燥的数学教材一大把，中共主要是俄系教材的原因\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-08",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 1,
      "discussions": [
        {
          "id": "1175815",
          "replier": {
